<font color="yellow">Batalkan! Batalkan!</font>

3
00:00:18,986 --> 00:00:22,655
<font color="yellow">Hentikan! Hentikan!</font>

4
00:00:22,986 --> 00:00:24,626
<font color="yellow">Itu dia! Keluar!</font>

5
00:00:24,626 --> 00:00:25,696
<font color="yellow">Keluar! Keluar!</font>

6
00:00:50,986 --> 00:00:53,116
<font color="yellow">- Lepaskan dia! Hentikan!
- Apa-apaan ini?</font>

7
00:00:53,116 --> 00:00:54,425
<font color="yellow">Apa-apaan?</font>

8
00:01:01,051 --> 00:01:03,752
<font color="yellow">Api? Bukan di sini.</font>

9
00:01:07,822 --> 00:01:08,822
<font color="yellow"><i>[Choi Joon Seok]</i></font>

10
00:01:21,072 --> 00:01:24,041
<font color="yellow">Kau membuatku gila! Kenapa kau meninggalkan anak-anak di sana?</font>

11
00:01:26,501 --> 00:01:27,572
<font color="yellow">Astaga!</font>

12
00:01:28,041 --> 00:01:29,242
<font color="yellow">Bajingan kau!</font>

13
00:01:29,242 --> 00:01:30,912
<font color="yellow">- Kuberi pelajaran kau!
- Di mana anak-anak itu?</font>

14
00:01:30,912 --> 00:01:32,341
<font color="yellow">Lepaskan! Lepaskan aku!</font>

15
00:01:32,341 --> 00:01:33,981
<font color="yellow">(Ungkap kebenaran! Katakan padaku mengapa anakku tewas!)</font>

16
00:01:33,981 --> 00:01:35,251
<font color="yellow">(Kalian sudah membunuh ratusan orang,
masih ingin membunuh lagi?)</font>

17
00:01:37,121 --> 00:01:38,882
<font color="yellow">- Aku akan memeriksa mereka. Pergilah.
- Baik.</font>

18
00:01:39,022 --> 00:01:41,552
<font color="yellow">Anak-anak. Anak-anak di mana?</font>

19
00:01:41,552 --> 00:01:44,022
<font color="yellow">- Di sana! Di sana!
- Astaga.</font>

20
00:01:44,022 --> 00:01:46,362
<font color="yellow">- Di mana? Di mana tepatnya?
- Astaga!</font>

21
00:01:55,001 --> 00:01:56,942
<font color="yellow">Permen Karet! Permen Karet!</font>

22
00:02:21,392 --> 00:02:23,492
<font color="yellow">Katamu kau suka rasa vanila, 'kan?</font>

23
00:02:23,862 --> 00:02:26,901
<font color="yellow">Tolong es krim vanila satu saja.</font>

24
00:02:26,901 --> 00:02:29,101
<font color="yellow">- Spagettinya--
- Kelihatannya, kalian bersenang-senang.</font>

25
00:02:29,101 --> 00:02:31,302
<font color="yellow">- Ya.
- Jadi, kalian bermain dengan boneka kalian?</font>

26
00:02:31,302 --> 00:02:32,341
<font color="yellow">Ya!</font>

27
00:02:32,341 --> 00:02:34,012
<font color="yellow">Orang tua kalian akan segera kembali.</font>

28
00:03:01,772 --> 00:03:03,371
<font color="yellow">- Apa-apaan?
- Benar-benar!</font>

29
00:03:23,492 --> 00:03:24,721
<font color="yellow">Lepaskan! Cukup, keparat!</font>

30
00:03:24,721 --> 00:03:25,992
<font color="yellow">Hentikan!</font>

31
00:03:26,422 --> 00:03:28,691
<font color="yellow">Hentikan! Hentikan, bangsat!</font>

32
00:03:29,792 --> 00:03:31,561
<font color="yellow">Aku polisi! HEI!</font>

33
00:03:33,702 --> 00:03:36,272
<font color="yellow">JANGAN BERGERAK KALIAN SEMUA BAJINGAN!</font>

34
00:03:36,272 --> 00:03:37,901
<font color="yellow">Kecuali kalian ingin aku melubangi kepala kalian.</font>

35
00:03:41,542 --> 00:03:42,672
<font color="yellow">Ke mana dia?</font>

36
00:03:46,811 --> 00:03:48,682
<font color="yellow">Apa? Siapa yang melakukannya?</font>

37
00:03:48,751 --> 00:03:50,422
<font color="yellow">Astaga, apa yang harus kulakukan?</font>

38
00:03:50,952 --> 00:03:52,422
<font color="yellow">Aih.</font>

39
00:03:52,522 --> 00:03:54,591
<font color="yellow">Hei! Hei!</font>

40
00:03:58,661 --> 00:03:59,862
<font color="yellow">Tolong bantu kami.</font>

41
00:04:00,091 --> 00:04:01,432
<font color="yellow">- Di sini.
- Anda baik-baik saja?</font>

42
00:04:01,432 --> 00:04:02,762
<font color="yellow">- Ada anak-anak di dalam.
- Anak-anak?</font>

43
00:04:03,362 --> 00:04:04,531
<font color="yellow">Astaga, apa yang harus kita lakukan?</font>

44
00:04:06,232 --> 00:04:09,001
<font color="yellow">Apa yang terjadi di sana? Bikin gila saja!</font>

45
00:04:27,121 --> 00:04:28,251
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana aku bisa membuka ini?</font>

46
00:04:30,461 --> 00:04:33,162
<font color="yellow">Oppa! Oppa! Tolong bantu aku.</font>

47
00:04:33,261 --> 00:04:35,492
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana ini? Aku tidak bisa membuka gembok ini.</font>

48
00:04:35,592 --> 00:04:37,631
<font color="yellow">Anak-anak ada di dalam. Bagaimana ini?</font>

49
00:04:38,961 --> 00:04:41,432
<font color="yellow"><i>Terlebih, mayoritas adalah jiwa anak-anak.</i></font>

50
00:04:41,932 --> 00:04:44,941
<font color="yellow"><i>Anak-anak yang tidak tahu alasan mereka harus mati.</i></font>

51
00:04:45,672 --> 00:04:47,871
<font color="yellow"><i>Anak-anak yang semestinya memiliki banyak waktu tersisa.</i></font>

52
00:04:48,311 --> 00:04:49,871
<font color="yellow"><i>Mengumpulkan jiwa anak-anak...</i></font>

53
00:04:49,871 --> 00:04:52,412
<font color="yellow"><i>...yang penuh dengan impian masa depan mereka,</i></font>

54
00:04:53,881 --> 00:04:55,581
<font color="yellow"><i>jelas bukanlah perkara mudah.</i></font>

55
00:04:55,581 --> 00:04:57,121
<font color="yellow">Tidak akan lama. Tunggu sebentar, ya?</font>

56
00:04:58,621 --> 00:04:59,881
<font color="yellow">Tidak boleh.</font>

57
00:05:00,552 --> 00:05:02,992
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak boleh terlibat dalam usaha menyelamatkan nyawa manusia.</font>

58
00:05:03,922 --> 00:05:05,222
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana ini?</font>

59
00:05:07,561 --> 00:05:09,862
<font color="yellow">Anak-anak, tunggu sebentar, ya.</font>

60
00:05:15,102 --> 00:05:16,172
<font color="yellow">Tidak boleh.</font>

61
00:05:16,172 --> 00:05:17,602
<font color="yellow"><i>Orang yang kehilangan pasangan akibat kematian...</i></font>

62
00:05:18,571 --> 00:05:20,472
<font color="yellow"><i>...disebut "duda" atau "janda".</i></font>

63
00:05:20,571 --> 00:05:23,612
<font color="yellow"><i>Dan anak-anak yang kehilangan orang tua mereka disebut yatim piatu.</i></font>

64
00:05:24,211 --> 00:05:25,682
<font color="yellow"><i>Tapi apa kau tahu sebutan...</i></font>

65
00:05:26,782 --> 00:05:28,482
<font color="yellow"><i>...bagi orang tua yang kehilangan anak mereka?</i></font>

66
00:05:28,912 --> 00:05:30,081
<font color="yellow"><i>Tidak ada.</i></font>

67
00:05:30,282 --> 00:05:31,881
<font color="yellow"><i>Begitu kejam rasanya...</i></font>

68
00:05:32,381 --> 00:05:34,552
<font color="yellow"><i>...hingga tak ada sebutan yang tepat.</i></font>

69
00:05:39,722 --> 00:05:40,831
<font color="yellow">Minggir!</font>

70
00:05:52,271 --> 00:05:53,302
<font color="yellow">Keluarlah!</font>

71
00:06:02,951 --> 00:06:04,581
<font color="yellow">TIDAK! BAGAIMANA INI!</font>

72
00:06:04,581 --> 00:06:05,581
<font color="yellow">Joon Seok-ah!</font>

73
00:06:05,982 --> 00:06:07,152
<font color="yellow">Cepat selamatkan mereka!</font>

74
00:06:07,821 --> 00:06:10,222
<font color="yellow">- Cepat!
- Putraku...</font>

75
00:06:10,422 --> 00:06:12,461
<font color="yellow">JOON SEOK!</font>

76
00:06:16,191 --> 00:06:17,201
<font color="yellow">- Apa yang terjadi? Apa-apaan ini?
- Pintunya terbuka.</font>

77
00:06:17,201 --> 00:06:19,061
<font color="yellow">- Keluarlah!
- Hubungi ambulans sekarang juga!</font>

78
00:06:19,432 --> 00:06:20,831
<font color="yellow">- Ayah...
- Kemarilah.</font>

79
00:06:23,172 --> 00:06:25,641
<font color="yellow">Di mana ambulansnya? Ambulansnya belum datang?</font>

80
00:06:25,742 --> 00:06:28,711
<font color="yellow">Joon Seok? Di mana Joon Seok?</font>

81
00:06:30,172 --> 00:06:31,982
<font color="yellow">Bukankah itu Ha Ram?</font>

82
00:06:32,542 --> 00:06:34,381
<font color="yellow">Kenapa dia ada di sini?</font>

83
00:06:35,652 --> 00:06:36,682
<font color="yellow">Ha Ram!</font>

84
00:06:41,021 --> 00:06:42,222
<font color="yellow">Permen Karet!</font>

85
00:06:43,722 --> 00:06:44,761
<font color="yellow">Ha Ram!</font>

86
00:06:45,422 --> 00:06:46,992
<font color="yellow">Joon Seok!</font>

87
00:06:46,992 --> 00:06:49,891
<font color="yellow">- Hei, minggir!
- Anakku masih ada di dalam sana.</font>

88
00:06:49,961 --> 00:06:51,061
<font color="yellow">Ha Ram!</font>

89
00:06:51,862 --> 00:06:53,032
<font color="yellow">Permen Karet!</font>

90
00:07:00,172 --> 00:07:01,271
<font color="yellow">Kemarilah.</font>

91
00:07:02,011 --> 00:07:03,811
<font color="yellow">Kemarilah. Keluar dari sana!</font>

92
00:07:04,381 --> 00:07:05,881
<font color="yellow">- Tidak mau.
- Aish.</font>

93
00:07:06,581 --> 00:07:07,912
<font color="yellow">Terserah kau saja.</font>

94
00:07:17,092 --> 00:07:18,662
<font color="yellow">Tak apa. Kemarilah. Ya?</font>

95
00:07:18,662 --> 00:07:20,761
<font color="yellow">- Tidak mau! Aku takut.
- Ayolah.</font>

96
00:07:20,761 --> 00:07:22,891
<font color="yellow">- Tak apa. Tak apa.
- Aku takut.</font>

97
00:07:23,032 --> 00:07:24,961
<font color="yellow">Keluarlah. Keluarlah.</font>

98
00:07:26,061 --> 00:07:28,771
<font color="yellow">Aigoo... bagus, Nak.</font>

99
00:07:28,771 --> 00:07:30,742
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, kau aman sekarang.</font>

100
00:07:30,972 --> 00:07:32,042
<font color="yellow">Keluarlah.</font>

101
00:07:37,282 --> 00:07:38,842
<font color="yellow">- Terima kasih.
- Keluarlah sekarang juga.</font>

102
00:07:38,941 --> 00:07:39,982
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

103
00:07:44,682 --> 00:07:45,782
<font color="yellow">Permen Karet!</font>

104
00:07:46,081 --> 00:07:47,792
<font color="yellow">- Joon Seok!
- Dia belum keluar.</font>

105
00:07:50,021 --> 00:07:51,061
<font color="yellow"><i>[Choi Joon Seok]</i></font>

106
00:07:52,391 --> 00:07:53,761
<font color="yellow">- Oppa.
- Ayo cepat keluar.</font>

107
00:07:53,761 --> 00:07:55,292
<font color="yellow">Ayahnya Hoon Seok masih di sini.</font>

108
00:07:55,292 --> 00:07:57,061
<font color="yellow">Bawa anak ini keluar dulu.</font>

109
00:07:57,061 --> 00:07:58,131
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

110
00:07:58,131 --> 00:07:59,631
<font color="yellow">Permen Karet! PERMEN KARET!</font>

111
00:08:00,771 --> 00:08:02,172
<font color="yellow">Kemarilah.</font>

112
00:08:03,232 --> 00:08:05,472
<font color="yellow">- Hei! Apa kau di sana?
- Permen Karet!</font>

113
00:08:06,042 --> 00:08:07,972
<font color="yellow">- Ayo, keluar!
- Oppa!</font>

114
00:08:08,112 --> 00:08:09,342
<font color="yellow">Tolonglah hentikan!</font>

115
00:08:09,441 --> 00:08:10,742
<font color="yellow">Kau bilang tidak ingin mati!</font>

116
00:08:10,742 --> 00:08:11,742
<font color="yellow">Sebentar saja.</font>

117
00:08:12,482 --> 00:08:14,451
<font color="yellow">- Permen Karet!
- Ajeossi!</font>

118
00:08:15,612 --> 00:08:16,782
<font color="yellow">Ajeossi!</font>

119
00:08:17,482 --> 00:08:19,552
<font color="yellow">Ajeossi! Bangunlah.</font>

120
00:08:21,951 --> 00:08:24,621
<font color="yellow">Bangunlah! Kau tidak boleh mati.</font>

121
00:08:24,891 --> 00:08:27,831
<font color="yellow">Kau harus menyelamatkan nyawa anakmu! Bangunlah!</font>

122
00:08:28,292 --> 00:08:29,391
<font color="yellow">Kemari.</font>

123
00:08:30,362 --> 00:08:33,132
<font color="yellow">Bangunlah! Kubilang bangunlah!</font>

124
00:08:33,532 --> 00:08:34,932
<font color="yellow">Cepat bangunlah!</font>

125
00:08:35,231 --> 00:08:37,101
<font color="yellow">- Permen Karet!
- Kau harus menyelamatkan nyawa anakmu!</font>

126
00:08:37,101 --> 00:08:38,872
<font color="yellow">- Permen Karet! Di mana kau?
- Oppa, aku di sini.</font>

127
00:08:39,002 --> 00:08:40,571
<font color="yellow">- Bantu dia.
- Keluar! Keluar dari sini!</font>

128
00:08:45,382 --> 00:08:46,682
<font color="yellow">Sebentar.</font>

129
00:08:47,152 --> 00:08:48,682
<font color="yellow">- Tolong aku.
- Keluar!</font>

130
00:08:48,851 --> 00:08:50,882
<font color="yellow">- Bawa anak ini dan keluarlah.
- Apa?</font>

131
00:08:52,652 --> 00:08:53,821
<font color="yellow">Ke mana kau?</font>

132
00:08:54,652 --> 00:08:56,392
<font color="yellow">- Kau di bawah sini?
- Tolong bantu aku.</font>

133
00:08:56,552 --> 00:08:58,461
<font color="yellow">- Sebentar.
- Di sini.</font>

134
00:09:02,191 --> 00:09:03,392
<font color="yellow">Astaga.</font>

135
00:09:11,902 --> 00:09:13,872
<font color="yellow">Keluar! Cepat!</font>

136
00:09:15,241 --> 00:09:16,772
<font color="yellow">Kita tidak boleh membiarkan mereka mati di sana.</font>

137
00:09:20,382 --> 00:09:22,882
<font color="yellow">- Baiklah.
- Kirim ambulans lebih banyak lagi.</font>

138
00:09:23,052 --> 00:09:25,522
<font color="yellow">- Kondisnya saat ini...
- Kirim ambulans tambahan sekarang!</font>

139
00:09:25,682 --> 00:09:27,552
<font color="yellow">Kalian hanya mengirim tiga!</font>

140
00:09:29,422 --> 00:09:31,622
<font color="yellow">- Bawa dia.
- Cepat!</font>

141
00:09:36,731 --> 00:09:38,132
<font color="yellow">Ambulannya di sana.</font>

142
00:09:39,461 --> 00:09:40,902
<font color="yellow">Rawat anak-anak dulu.</font>

143
00:09:41,372 --> 00:09:43,741
<font color="yellow">Lakukan seperti ini. Dari samping. Perlahan-lahan.</font>

144
00:09:44,071 --> 00:09:46,402
<font color="yellow">- Hei, kemarilah.
- Apakah wajahnya cedera parah?</font>

145
00:09:49,341 --> 00:09:51,711
<font color="yellow">Kau baik-baik saja? Apa kau terluka?</font>

146
00:09:52,441 --> 00:09:55,412
<font color="yellow">Ada apa denganmu? Tidak seperti dirimu biasanya sampai
menyelamatkan seorang anak.</font>

147
00:09:55,412 --> 00:09:58,522
<font color="yellow">Lalu? Tidak ada satupun orang tua yang akan berjalan pergi
begitu saja...</font>

148
00:09:58,522 --> 00:10:01,451
<font color="yellow">...ketika ada seorang anak yang sekarat di depan mereka!</font>

149
00:10:03,052 --> 00:10:05,662
<font color="yellow">Omong-omong, sedang apa kau di sini?</font>

150
00:10:05,762 --> 00:10:06,762
<font color="yellow">Bukan urusanmu.</font>

151
00:10:07,731 --> 00:10:11,061
<font color="yellow">Oh ya, Hoon Seok menunggu donor sumsum darimu.
Kau harus bergegas.</font>

152
00:10:12,201 --> 00:10:13,731
<font color="yellow">Oh, ya, terima kasih.</font>

153
00:10:21,741 --> 00:10:24,741
<font color="yellow">Kau bilang moto hidupmu adalah 'tidak pernah mati', 'kan?</font>

154
00:10:26,081 --> 00:10:28,981
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana bisa kau seceroboh ini bila
berkaitan dengan nyawamu sendiri?</font>

155
00:10:29,081 --> 00:10:30,081
<font color="yellow">Lihat yang sudah kaulakukan hari ini!</font>

156
00:10:30,382 --> 00:10:33,422
<font color="yellow">Kau melompat ke dalam api berkali-kali untuk menyelamatkan
orang lain.</font>

157
00:10:33,851 --> 00:10:35,821
<font color="yellow">Kau bisa mati sendiri kalau terus begitu.</font>

158
00:10:38,861 --> 00:10:41,061
<font color="yellow">Aku benar-benar tidak bisa memahamimu.</font>

159
00:10:41,461 --> 00:10:44,932
<font color="yellow">Semua orang takut akan kematian, 'kan? Kau tidak?</font>

160
00:10:46,502 --> 00:10:50,272
<font color="yellow">Mana ada coba manusia yang tidak takut mati?
Aku juga takut.</font>

161
00:10:50,941 --> 00:10:52,002
<font color="yellow">Tetap saja...</font>

162
00:10:54,042 --> 00:10:56,882
<font color="yellow">...ketakutan itu tidak lebih besar dibandingkan rasa takut...</font>

163
00:10:57,581 --> 00:10:59,981
<font color="yellow">...melihat orang lain tewas di depan mataku.</font>

164
00:11:05,321 --> 00:11:06,451
<font color="yellow">Berikan.</font>

165
00:11:09,022 --> 00:11:10,262
<font color="yellow">Diam sajalah!</font>

166
00:11:11,461 --> 00:11:13,561
<font color="yellow">Wajahmu yang sudah jelek jadi kelihatan makin buruk rupa.</font>

167
00:11:15,262 --> 00:11:16,662
<font color="yellow">- Astaga.
- Apa-apaan semua ini?</font>

168
00:11:23,601 --> 00:11:26,201
<font color="yellow">Tutup matamu! Bisa-bisa nanti kena matamu!</font>

169
00:11:26,941 --> 00:11:28,012
<font color="yellow">Tutup mata!</font>

170
00:11:36,111 --> 00:11:37,282
<font color="yellow">Kenapa?</font>

171
00:11:38,221 --> 00:11:39,951
<font color="yellow">Satu ambulans baru saja meninggalkan lokasi.</font>

172
00:11:40,221 --> 00:11:41,392
<font color="yellow">Tidak ada.</font>

173
00:11:43,451 --> 00:11:45,262
<font color="yellow">Bersihkan sendiri saja. Ini.</font>

174
00:11:45,922 --> 00:11:47,262
<font color="yellow">Memangnya kau tidak punya tangan, ya?</font>

175
00:11:49,032 --> 00:11:52,162
<font color="yellow">Apa-apaan coba? Dia sendiri yang tadi ingin melakukannya.
Pikirannya berubah-ubah sekali, sih!</font>

176
00:11:56,172 --> 00:11:57,741
<font color="yellow">Kami tidak melakukannya.</font>

177
00:11:57,802 --> 00:12:00,142
<font color="yellow">Sungguh. Kami tidak pernah mengunci pintu itu,</font>

178
00:12:00,142 --> 00:12:01,772
<font color="yellow">dan tidak memulai kebakaran juga.</font>

179
00:12:01,772 --> 00:12:03,811
<font color="yellow">Tolong jawab saja pertanyaanku.</font>

180
00:12:04,581 --> 00:12:06,542
<font color="yellow">- Sebentar.
- Astaga, ayolah. Benar-benar.</font>

